high_descs: turn right, take a step, turn left, walk to stove, turn left, take a few steps, turn left to face counter
pick up the bowl that is on the counter
turn left, walk forward, turn right, walk to fridge
put bowl in fridge, wait a minute, take bowl out
turn around, take two steps, turn right to face sink
put the bowl in the cabinet below to the right of the sink
anns.task_desc: put a cold bowl in the cabinet

high_descs: Chill the bowl in the fridge.
Grab the bowl back and walk to the sink.
Place the bowl in the cupboard.
anns.task_desc: Chill a bowl and put it in the cupboard.

high_descs: Turn right, walk around the silver counter to the left and turn left to face the silver counter.
Pick up the clear container in front of the loaf of bread on the counter.
Turn left and hang a right to the black fridge.
Put the container inside the fridge on the bottom shelf, chill it, remove it and close the door.
Turn around and face the cabinets under the counter to the right.
Open the far right cabinet, place the chilled container inside and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled container in a cabinet.
